        Bob->>Network: Publish Tree {<br/>  Root (entity_id: Bob)<br/>    Non-Slot Node: "Partnerships"<br/>      Contributors: [Carol: 40pts, Kitchen: 30pts]<br/>    Goal: "Nutrition"<br/>      Need-Slot: {food, declared: 90}<br/>}
    and
        Carol->>Network: Publish Tree {<br/>  Root (entity_id: Carol)<br/>    Goal: "Community Kitchen"<br/>      Capacity-Slot: {food, available: 150}<br/>        Contributors: [] (self only)
