            Note over Carol: DerivedStateMap[Carol] = {<br/>  shareMap: {Alice: 0.429, Bob: 0.571},<br/>  mutualSatisfactionMap: {Alice: 0.429, Bob: 0.571}<br/>}
        end
    and
        rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
            Note over Kitchen: 📊 RECOMPUTE DERIVED STATE (Reactive)
