    Note over Alice,Network: ═══════════ TREE AGGREGATION: SATISFACTION FLOWS UP ═══════════
    Note over Alice,Network: 📈 structure.md: Hierarchical satisfaction aggregation<br/>Need-Slot → Capacity-Slot → Goal → Root

    par Parallel Satisfaction Aggregation (Automatic, Reactive)
        rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
            Note over Carol: 📊 HIERARCHICAL AGGREGATION (Automatic)
            Carol->>Carol: Observe satisfaction from network:<br/><br/>Capacity-Slot satisfaction (weighted by child weights):<br/>  Alice allocation: 64.3 × 0.85 = 54.7<br/>  Bob allocation: 45 × 0.40 = 18<br/>  Total accepted: 64.3 + 45 = 109.3<br/>  <br/>  Capacity-Slot sat = (54.7 + 18) / 109.3 = 0.665<br/><br/>Goal satisfaction (from capacity slot):<br/>  Goal sat = 0.665 (propagated up)<br/><br/>Root satisfaction (from goal):<br/>  Root sat = 0.665<br/><br/>💡 Satisfaction propagates UP the tree!
            Note over Carol: DerivedStateMap[Carol] updated:<br/>capacity_slot.satisfaction = 0.665<br/>goal.satisfaction = 0.665<br/>root.satisfaction = 0.665
        end
    and
        rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
            Note over Kitchen: 📊 HIERARCHICAL AGGREGATION (Automatic)
            Kitchen->>Kitchen: Observe satisfaction from network:<br/><br/>Capacity-Slot satisfaction:<br/>  Alice: 35.7 × 0.95 = 33.9<br/>  Bob: 45 × 0.90 = 40.5<br/>  Total: 35.7 + 45 = 80.7<br/><br/>  Capacity-Slot sat = (33.9 + 40.5) / 80.7 = 0.921<br/><br/>Goal satisfaction:<br/>  Goal sat = 0.921<br/><br/>Root satisfaction:<br/>  Root sat = 0.921<br/><br/>✅ High satisfaction (excellent quality!)
            Note over Kitchen: DerivedStateMap[Kitchen] updated:<br/>capacity_slot.satisfaction = 0.921<br/>goal.satisfaction = 0.921<br/>root.satisfaction = 0.921
